SUMMARY:Muddy Run Recreation Park Field Trip
DESCRIPTION:Larry Bernhardt will lead a field trip to Muddy Run Recreation Park near Holtwood. Meet at the last parking lot on the left past the Ryan Observatory by 7 a.m. The following GPS coordinates can be used for the parking area: 39.8446000\, -76.2828612. The walk will cover 3 total miles (out and back) and look for spring migrants and anything that may be on the lake. Contact Larry at 717-314-1461 or sjbernhardt@verizon.net by 6 p.m. the previous day if you plan to attend. \nMeeting Location: Muddy Run Recreation Park\, Holtwood\, Pa. 17532 (Use coordinates for the last parking lot on the left past the Ryan Observatory: 39.8446000\, -76.2828612)\nContact: Larry Bernhardt\, 717-314-1461 or sjbernhardt@verizon.net
