SUMMARY:Millport Conservancy Field Trip
DESCRIPTION:Doug Anderson will lead a field trip through Millport Conservancy. Meet at 7 a.m. in the main parking area located just off 737 E Millport Rd.\, Lititz. This will be an easy morning walk through the Conservancy trail along Lititz Run to identify a variety of target species including warblers and wading birds. Bring binoculars\, water and snacks. Contact Doug at 717-203-2482 or douglas.anderson58@yahoo.com with questions or call by 6 p.m. the night before if you plan to attend. \nMeeting Location: Millport Conservancy\, 737 E Millport Rd.\, Lititz\, PA 17543\nContact: Doug Anderson\, 717-203-2482 or douglas.anderson58@yahoo.com 
